string.text: Changing currency will NOT convert values of existing transactions.
Thank you for trying out Budget Planner!
This simple tool will help you estimate expenses and earnings over time and plan your spendings. To start, please enter your current balance and base currency.
"Over time your balance may get significantly off due to accumulated error. You can adjust it by clicking 'adjust balance' button on the main screen."
Next you will need to add the rest of your periodic expenses and income. After this is done, you will be able to check your future balance estimation, see statistics and add planned spendings.
Add some periodic income and payments. These are some examples to get you started, you may skip any of them.
